nodes.text: Star Wars Insider Exclusive Collector's Issue

The Star Wars Insider Exclusive Collector's Issue was given out free starting on September 21, 2004 by Best Buy to customers who purchased either the original trilogy on DVD or LucasArts' Star Wars: Battlefront.
